    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/1605"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Hludouuicus</persName> divina favente gratia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Notum sit omnibus sanctae dei ecclesiae
                        fidelibus nostrisque presentibus scilicet et futuris, qualiter dilecta nepta
                        nostra <persName ref="#people/242">Hirmingarda</persName> deprecata est
                        celsitudinem nostram, ut ob mercedis nostrae augmentum quasdam <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">res proprietatis nostrae</rs>
                        consistentes in <rs key="#Geographic_regions">Italia</rs> ei in proprium
                        concedissemus. Cuius petitioni ob amorem domini nostri iesu christi libenti
                        animo assensum prebentes decrevimus ita fieri. Concessimus itaque ei illam
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> in proprium quae vocatur <geogName
                            ref="#estates/222"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Morcula</geogName> consistentem in <geogName ref="#estates/270"
                            key="#Comitatus"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/10">Pergama</placeName></geogName> et <placeName
                            ref="#places/1916"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/1516"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >Lemin</geogName></placeName> curtem in eodem comitatu et <placeName
                            ref="#places/596"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Curtem maiorem</placeName> in <geogName ref="#estates/105"
                            key="#Comitatus"><placeName ref="#places/43" key="#Cities"
                                >Placentina</placeName> comitatu</geogName> et in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/277"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Aucia</geogName> et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1416"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Monasteries"
                            >novum monasterium</orgName> in <placeName ref="#places/65"
                            >Papia</placeName>. Et iussimus ei fieri hoc nostrae auctoritatis
                        praeceptum, per quod decernimus atque iubemus, ut nec nos nec ullus ex
                        successoribus nostris ullam potestatem habeat de prefatis rebus ei quicquam
                        auferre, sed eas cum omnibus ibidem adiacentiis vel pertinentibus diebus
                        vitae suae securiter habeat teneat atque possideat; post suum vero obitum ad
                        suae filiae revertatur potestatem. Et ut haec auctoritas largitionis nostrae
                        firmior habeatur et per futura tempora a fidelibus nostris verius credatur
                        et diligentius observetur, manu propria nostra subter eam firmavimus et
                        anuli nostri inpressione assignari iussimus. Signum (MF.) domni Hludouuici
                        serenissimi regis.   <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Eberardus"
                                >Hebarhardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor"><name ref="Liutbertus">Liutberti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicappellani</rs> recognovi et (SR. NN.) (SI. 2)
                          Data iiii kal. mar. anno xxxviii regni domni Hludouuici serenissimi regis
                        in <rs key="#Geographic_regions">orientali Francia</rs> regnante, indictio
                        viii; actum <placeName ref="#places/1917">Franconofurt</placeName>; in dei
                        nomine feliciter amen</ab>
                </div>
